{"tid":1210530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位走啦..好唔好","createTime":"2019-06-12T13:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T17:12:03.000Z","uid":18577,"like":980,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"978c7d79ab29092be0d6e20288b11cb851e6736e","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:58:08.000Z","msg":"我明白大家都覺得好唔甘心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但真係走啦<br />\n依家留低都起唔到作用<br />\n不如留力返屋企睇下之後再有咩行動啦<br />\n唔好作犧牲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個都不能少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5bc086fa4475fc13b2a7155be1180bc2efff6c","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":11,"dislike":7,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:58:17.000Z","msg":"走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd56fc3813315222284cfc1e6bde27db1801ca9","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8818760e2c9a8f0f8823f8f7b13648a87cefb43b","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:00:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be84ebd510c944ac942aa2c1ad2f42012c4289aa","tid":1210530,"uid":167277,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:01:02.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"39d5843f60cb01003f0377704be660b243e584ef","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e03fa47062972ce25d4c634c82ce58ac1f5aaa","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:01:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c67551024538be4f86d1a3f3decfea39946bd9d","tid":1210530,"uid":233929,"like":215,"dislike":2,"score":213,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:02:18.000Z","msg":"走<br />\n<br />\n經過今日一戰，大家心情一定好嬲好沈重。<br />\n但大家都忘記左be water 既原則，五年前既雨革已經知道拖長黎玩一定會輸。<br />\n我文筆好差，只講重點，其他留返比起巴絲補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先，保持冷靜，冷靜，冷靜<br />\n唔好比怒氣蓋過你地既頭腦<br />\n<br />\n1. 今日流會目的已達到，立會依家只係一個無意義既地標。<br />\n<br />\n2. 就算條街一個人都冇，班黑警點都要繼續留守，可以消耗佢地體力，又補充到自己人既力量<br />\n<br />\n3. 主流意見係我地到，要再佔路都係幾架私家車的事，隨時隨地可以再戰<br />\n<br />\n4. 夜晚一定有鬼，依家8點幾9點個個放左工過哂黎都唔衝，要等入夜先衝？<br />\n<br />\n我自己琴晚10點出黎守到今朝有人黎左再返工，6點放工又過黎守到依家，我相信好多好多巴絲同我一樣，真係好攰好攰，今次要贏絕對唔可以日日係到鳩企。<br />\n<br />\nBe Water My Friends"},{"pid":"fb8bf4431c25b26a3dce5a14df68fb8afde56335","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"入夜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好危險啦<br />\n走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3991c4ed1f1f4472881eb26b5df3e5aa1ddd5be3","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:08:14.000Z","msg":"走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6e630151cf8b40ddf6e0d7bde9f378f96d1b0a","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:09:35.000Z","msg":"走啦<img src=\"/assets/fa