0530,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:40:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2047b95310e16211dbc90f441a37534fa76431d9","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:41:15.000Z","msg":"走呀"},{"pid":"149928f893eac7e20d5bc4679a8c5efbad2e5769","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2c945afa4e6e6b169700e38f9ab3afc81ff02a","tid":1210530,"uid":92476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c67551024538be4f86d1a3f3decfea39946bd9d","tid":1210530,"uid":233929,"like":215,"dislike":2,"score":213,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:02:18.000Z","msg":"走<br />\n<br />\n經過今日一戰，大家心情一定好嬲好沈重。<br />\n但大家都忘記左be water 既原則，五年前既雨革已經知道拖長黎玩一定會輸。<br />\n我文筆好差，只講重點，其他留返比起巴絲補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先，保持冷靜，冷靜，冷靜<br />\n唔好比怒氣蓋過你地既頭腦<br />\n<br />\n1. 今日流會目的已達到，立會依家只係一個無意義既地標。<br />\n<br />\n2. 就算條街一個人都冇，班黑警點都要繼續留守，可以消耗佢地體力，又補充到自己人既力量<br />\n<br />\n3. 主流意見係我地到，要再佔路都係幾架私家車的事，隨時隨地可以再戰<br />\n<br />\n4. 夜晚一定有鬼，依家8點幾9點個個放左工過哂黎都唔衝，要等入夜先衝？<br />\n<br />\n我自己琴晚10點出黎守到今朝有人黎左再返工，6點放工又過黎守到依家，我相信好多好多巴絲同我一樣，真係好攰好攰，今次要贏絕對唔可以日日係到鳩企。<br />\n<br />\nBe Water My Friends"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:41:51.000Z","msg":"你好好休息一下"},{"pid":"71ac31991ec76f3f540bcb5fbdc42228bee83eab","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:42:39.000Z","msg":"走呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d6a6f58ad208555b8607567d3f4176ca749c51","tid":1210530,"uid":143171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"