要打國際輿論戰？<br />\n自己香港自己救<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n民陣我屌你老母啦<br />\n玩口號<br />\n叫人散水<br />\n叫人夜晚圍夜晚衝無人嘅政府大樓<br />\n又搞大台<br />\n<br />\n仆街啦去"},{"pid":"58fcc38248c2f108f49831b72bc8d94f7ecaf629","tid":1210530,"uid":149026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:50:38.000Z","msg":"物質已經開始慢慢撤，唔好再買物資啦！除非有人交更如果唔係根本冇得鬥長命！"},{"pid":"aea3255167f03bd88f67070cf33e6d2d6ee98751","tid":1210530,"uid":33325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:51:02.000Z","msg":"走，班狗日頭咁多人睇住都咁痴線，一入夜我驚你渣都冇得剩，佢哋又有物質又有轉更無限血點夠佢嚟。<br />\n<br />\n佔領唔係唯一方法，正如其他巴打講，我好相信今日之後會有好多唔同型式嘅行動向賣港嘅人施壓。<br />\n<br />\n其實你地今日已經贏晒，呢件事已經得到國際關注，我相信班賣港PK點都有壓力。<br />\n<br />\n令人心痛嘅喺受傷同被拘捕咗嘅義士，依家退落嚟雖然喺好唔服氣，但真心唔想再有無謂犧牲。"},{"pid":"d57fa70a87d6355f8f4fd9efd8d73cf2e65a8e2a","tid":1210530,"uid":43806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:52:43.000Z","msg":"班撚樣冇人性 <br />\n但係走 聽日仲有冇人敢出"},{"pid":"ac3c7f2a1fe07b10851f5ad8f6b172b0ff824660","tid":1210530,"uid":60936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:53:12.000Z","msg":"似又深夜玩困獸鬥"},{"pid":"b764a05171b8377b8dfc5376c3569b1bec675474","tid":1210530,"uid":139676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:53:27.000Z","msg":"好想返屋企食阿嫲煮既飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54dc8b8fe455cc740a83c83b5406bd720e1774ee","tid":1210530,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d57fa70a87d6355f8f4fd9efd8d73cf2e65a8e2a","tid":1210530,"uid":43806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:52:43.000Z","msg":"班撚樣冇人性 <br />\n但係走 聽日仲有冇人敢出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:54:30.000Z","msg":"你唔好妄想聽日有今日咁多人<br />\n今晚一定全清<br />\n你一句說話令佢地戀戰"},{"pid":"a770bba7cf8974f769a4b2f6d7314ce989194f59","tid":1210530,"uid":23590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:55:04.000Z","msg":"be water"},{"pid":"af15e1783173dfd2845ccdf9b5cc546710a04982","tid":1210530,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:57:40.000Z","msg":"多個人就做到好多嘢，冇咗就少個人做，請立即離開啦"},{"pid":"5fbb87fb76759095b393ecd8a50d6067e8ac5704","tid":1210530,"uid":25424,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:58:04.000Z","msg":"走啦<br />\n班警察已經癲左，用唔對等既武力<br />\n人地正常做法<br />\n示威者出汽油彈對付警察，警察先用催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n去到通街燒野搶舖，危害普通平民，先會用橡膠子彈<br />\n<br />\n依家明明只係示威者對警察，目標明確，都已經射橡膠子彈<br />\n同獨裁國家既軍警已經無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a24aee4c614083e71f3932a0b9e85b83b3eaec","tid":1210530,"uid":8265,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:58:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f556e0394d7447d3a2d57c8e8bee2a1f42dd95c","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:59:14.000Z","msg":"走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade0d769f66221cc7134642f25a017f6afd18234","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:59:54.000Z","msg":"走啦"},{"pid":"fff00ea3e3b03c5ebc77745730b3469c2f33531d","tid":1210530,"uid":111903,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:00:15.000Z","msg":"走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11158c75f17cc0df8f0b636e7c06803c7d128eb3","tid":1210530,"uid":230271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:01:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d3e34b7ffcf13f0b75ae45fc97b2bdef73fda661","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:01:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">在場既人走個陣叫埋大家走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"9ab88826936fce983decc10029a7e33c9fdecabf","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:01:30.000Z","msg":"走呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d14ca3fed111a0871fd3af1c770fe7ef361d421","tid":1210530,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:02:58.000Z","msg":"走啦, 訓個好覺啦"},{"pid":"73315b975e14d1d491f592ef7f39032b6e18bb9f","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:03:36.000Z","msg":"走呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ac3b319979daeff003d07502ef2544db4c6132f","tid":1210530,"uid":11550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:04:06.000Z","msg":"夜晚無咁多人睇住，逐批逐批俾人分開，打到豬頭咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返去抖下先，安全要緊"},{"pid":"206630ac370f59a69cf2d28de1756c6349d0f763","tid":1210530,"uid":37042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:04:10.000Z","msg":"明天再戰"},{"pid":"f6a8fc9727ff880d0b2964c18e238a2f0394f0a7","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:04:38.000Z","msg":"一入夜就真係危險好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484c35a3fe2a4deda6acee74cea72609dbe6d4c3","tid":1210530,"uid":114897,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:06:17.000Z","msg":"大家 而家走係為左行更遠的路呀<br />\n<br />\n今日我都喺金鐘<br />\n見到好多年青人好熱血 真係好感動<br />\n但都好多人受傷 真係好心痛呀<br />\n大家返去休息下  再見機行事好冇呀<br />\n唔想第一日就見到你地傷哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc731cc78af7646ae87aa1dbca999c8ce324f5b8","tid":1210530,"uid":256105,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:06:17.000Z","msg":"走啦，我地冇輸，留力下一回合。"},{"pid":"07db7db415376e69767b9d994fe913e3b9247f67","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:06:35.000Z","msg":"走呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076073cdb52f332ee9eced7591a9c08d39439b01","tid":1210530,"uid":114217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:07:13.000Z","msg":"今晚磨落去真係無意思<br />\n睇直播見佢地同黑警講道理<br />\n當堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501b39a9c40a95df9280485b7c9ae04dd42eaeca","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:07:37.000Z","msg":"走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3baf33fd12999532f4efdfb20829eaf025b477eb","tid":1210530,"uid":185914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:08:15.000Z","msg":"同意 大家經過今日都辛苦喇<br />\n希望各位可以抖抖 同屋企人報個平安<br />\n各位既平安係最重要!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n禁多位要冇事啊"},{"pid":"c68d8220b27a04f49361d087cde6bf28a9f00f5f","tid":1210530,"uid":164634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:11:43.000Z","msg":"如你手上有關於今天(2019年6月12日) 香港警察對市民 記者 議員 使用不必要的暴力的圖片 影片 聲音檔案 請用以下方法發送到各大媒體! 請廣傳!<br />\n<br />\n    If you have any visual evidence or audio recordings of Hong Kong police exerting excessive and unnecessary violence on protesting Hong Kong citizens, journalists, and legislative officials today (9th June. 2019), please send them to the media attached below! Please spread this message!<br />\n<br />\n    BBC News<br />\n    WhatsApp: +44 7555 173285<br />\n    Email: yourpics@bbc.co.uk<br />\n<br />\n    NBC NEWS<br />\n    WhatsApp: +1-646-858-9310<br />\n    Telegram: +1-646-858-9310<br />\n    Email: tips@nbcuni.com<br />\n<br />\n    The Guardian<br />\n    Whatsapp: +44 7867 825056"},{"pid":"d268f31f9a51a376b6c8554b43e259a371f110a0","tid":1210530,"uid":47776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:16:38.000Z","msg":"快啲叫佢地走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日唔想再見到有義士被捕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心情都跌到落谷底<br />\n留返條命過兩日再黎過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec6d9b2c9b750293f6bc612bd779ee2278fbf47","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:17:05.000Z","msg":"走呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a58d0550934646e9fb163b854d99ef2c71183c","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:17:24.000Z","msg":"走啦好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40499c5153345b877f0bf7648b7c8ff08ed4ee1b","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:18:22.000Z","msg":"走呀"},{"pid":"5a37cacc1ca847b17676faeb88a8471322ebcded","tid":1210530,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:19:35.000Z","msg":"好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a53391c35b518bb7f05aa44413def5d25051de6","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:21:26.000Z","msg":"走啦"},{"pid":"13b7c94d461d79d7c0b6a4abd1f20d981ff39dd5","tid":1210530,"uid":18577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:22:51.000Z","msg":"走呀"}]}